{"title":"如何終止當前使用本地主機上的端口的進程","uid":"8322e7bebc4ea10314b03d090995ff47","slug":"how-to-kill-port","date":"2021-11-21T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2021-11-24T17:08:19.790Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/how-to-kill-port.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2013/07/13/13/41/bash-161382_1280.png","content":"<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">發生什麼事？</p>\n<p>在進行本地開發時，需要透過本地端口建立伺服器連線進行預覽或測試，碰到端口(port)佔用時該如何解決呢？</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"For-Windows-user\"><a href=\"#For-Windows-user\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"For Windows user\"></a>For Windows user</h3><h4 id=\"Step-1-找到佔用此端口的進程PID\"><a href=\"#Step-1-找到佔用此端口的進程PID\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Step 1 找到佔用此端口的進程PID\"></a>Step 1 找到佔用此端口的進程PID</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">netstat</span> -ano <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> findstr:PortNumber<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>想知道更多關於: <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/windows-server/administration/windows-commands/netstat\">netstat</a>、<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/windows-server/administration/windows-commands/findstr\">findstr</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"Step-2-清除該進程\"><a href=\"#Step-2-清除該進程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Step 2 清除該進程\"></a>Step 2 清除該進程</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ taskkill /PID typeyourPIDhere /F<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>想知道更多關於: <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/windows-server/administration/windows-commands/taskkill\">taskkill</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"For-Unix-user\"><a href=\"#For-Unix-user\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"For Unix user\"></a>For Unix user</h3><h4 id=\"Step-1-找到佔用此端口的進程PID-1\"><a href=\"#Step-1-找到佔用此端口的進程PID-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Step 1 找到佔用此端口的進程PID\"></a>Step 1 找到佔用此端口的進程PID</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">lsof</span> -i:PortNumber <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>想知道更多關於: <a href=\"https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man8/lsof.8.html\">lsof</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"Step-2-清除該進程-1\"><a href=\"#Step-2-清除該進程-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Step 2 清除該進程\"></a>Step 2 清除該進程</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">kill</span> typeyourPIDhere <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>想知道更多關於: <a href=\"https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man1/kill.1.html\">kill</a></p>\n","text":" 發生什麼事？ 在進行本地開發時，需要透過本地端口建立伺服器連線進行預覽或測試，碰到端口(port)佔用時該如何解決呢？ For Windows userStep 1 找到佔用此端口的進程PID$ netstat -ano | findstr:PortNumber 想知道更多關於...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":352,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Devops","slug":"Devops","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Devops.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Windows","slug":"Windows","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Windows.json"},{"name":"Mac","slug":"Mac","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Mac.json"},{"name":"Unix","slug":"Unix","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Unix.json"},{"name":"Bash","slug":"Bash","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Bash.json"},{"name":"遇到問題就解決","slug":"遇到問題就解決","count":2,"path":"api/tags/遇到問題就解決.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#For-Windows-user\"><span class=\"toc-text\">For Windows user</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Step-1-%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%94%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%A4%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%80%B2%E7%A8%8BPID\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Step 1 找到佔用此端口的進程PID</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Step-2-%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4%E8%A9%B2%E9%80%B2%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Step 2 清除該進程</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#For-Unix-user\"><span class=\"toc-text\">For Unix user</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Step-1-%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%94%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%A4%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%80%B2%E7%A8%8BPID-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Step 1 找到佔用此端口的進程PID</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Step-2-%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4%E8%A9%B2%E9%80%B2%E7%A8%8B-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Step 2 清除該進程</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"炭吉貓","slug":"blog-author","ava